---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Pay and settle one existing incoming request

Usage: accept [OPTIONS] <REQUEST_ID>

Arguments:
  <REQUEST_ID>
          Canonical incoming request ID

Options:
      --from <METHOD_ID>
          Payment-method ID shown by `payment-methods list`

      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

  -h, --help
          Print help
